article.headline: Colgate 70, Navy 62
article.story: HAMILTON, N.Y. (AP) -- Jon Simon scored 24 points to lead Colgate in a 70-62 win over Navy Saturday. Kyle Chones scored 14 points and Kendall Chones added 10 for Colgate (10-18, 5-9 Patriot League). Greg Sprink had 29 points to lead Navy (14-15, 4-10) and Kaleo Kina contributed 13. Colgate led 33-26 at the half in a game they dominated. Navy led only once, by 3 points in the first half. The Raiders led by as many as 12 points in the first. Colgate outrebounded Navy 38-22. Navy finished with a 48.1 percent shooting average, while Colgate shot at 42.3 percent.
